## Directory Structure

```
/srv/woosoo/
├── nexus/          ← woosoo-nexus Laravel app (git clone)
├── pwa/            ← tablet-ordering-pwa built dist/ files
├── backups/        ← nightly MariaDB dumps
├── setup/          ← tablet onboarding HTML + ca.crt
└── certs/          ← mkcert TLS cert + key

/etc/woosoo/
└── .env            ← production env (root:www-data 640), symlinked to /srv/woosoo/nexus/.env

/etc/nginx/sites-available/woosoo   ← nginx vhost config
/etc/supervisor/conf.d/woosoo.conf  ← supervisor workers
/etc/dnsmasq.conf                   ← LAN DNS
/var/log/woosoo/                    ← supervisor worker logs
```

