### Phase 9 — App Deployment (woosoo-nexus)

**[MANDATORY]**

```bash
sudo mkdir -p /srv/woosoo/nexus
sudo git clone https://github.com/tech-artificer/woosoo-nexus.git /srv/woosoo/nexus
sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /srv/woosoo/nexus

# bootstrap/cache must exist (not in git)
sudo mkdir -p /srv/woosoo/nexus/bootstrap/cache
sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /srv/woosoo/nexus/bootstrap

# Install dependencies
sudo -u www-data composer install --no-dev --optimize-autoloader \
  --working-dir=/srv/woosoo/nexus

# Generate app key — temporarily allow www-data to write .env
sudo chmod 660 /etc/woosoo/.env
sudo -u www-data php /srv/woosoo/nexus/artisan key:generate
sudo chmod 640 /etc/woosoo/.env

# Migrate
sudo -u www-data php /srv/woosoo/nexus/artisan migrate --force

# Cache (MANDATORY after every .env or config change)
sudo -u www-data php /srv/woosoo/nexus/artisan config:cache
sudo -u www-data php /srv/woosoo/nexus/artisan route:cache
sudo -u www-data php /srv/woosoo/nexus/artisan view:cache

# Build frontend assets (MANDATORY — without this /login returns 500 Vite manifest not found)
# Run as current user (NOT sudo) to avoid node_modules permission errors
sudo mkdir -p /srv/woosoo/nexus/public/build
sudo chown woosoo:woosoo /srv/woosoo/nexus/public/build
cd /srv/woosoo/nexus
npm ci
sudo chmod 644 /etc/woosoo/.env && npm run build && sudo chmod 640 /etc/woosoo/.env
sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /srv/woosoo/nexus/public/build
sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /srv/woosoo/nexus/node_modules
```

> **NOTE:** After `config:cache` is active, `env()` calls outside config files return null. All env reads must go through `config()`. The codebase already follows this — do not call `env()` in app code.

