### Phase 12 — Tablet Setup Page

**File:** `/srv/woosoo/setup/index.html`

Served over plain HTTP at `http://<Pi-IP>/setup`. No TLS required — tablets need this before trusting the CA cert.

Content must include:
1. Link to download `/ca.crt`
2. Instructions to install CA cert on Android (Settings → Security → Install cert)
3. Instructions to set tablet WiFi DNS to Pi's IP
4. Final step: open `https://woosoo.local`

