## Verification Checklist

Run after full deployment:

```bash
# 1. Laravel health
curl -sk https://woosoo.local/up -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}\n"
# Expected: 200

# 2. API config endpoint (used by print-bridge relay tablet)
curl -sk https://woosoo.local/api/config
# Expected: {"broadcasting":{"driver":"reverb","key":"...","host":"woosoo.local","port":443,"scheme":"https",...}}

# 3. WebSocket reachable (400 = Reverb up but rejected non-WS curl — correct)
curl -sk https://woosoo.local/app/<REVERB_APP_KEY> -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}\n"
# Expected: 400

# 4. Supervisor workers
sudo supervisorctl status
# Expected: all 4 RUNNING

# 5. Krypton DB
sudo -u www-data php /srv/woosoo/nexus/artisan tinker
>>> DB::connection('pos')->select('SELECT 1');
# Expected: result set (no exception)

# 6. nginx DNS resolution
ping -c 1 woosoo.local
# Expected: resolves to Pi's IP
```

Browser checks:
- [ ] `https://woosoo.local/up` → "Application up"
- [ ] `https://woosoo.local/admin` → Filament admin panel
- [ ] `https://woosoo.local/horizon` → Horizon dashboard
- [ ] `https://woosoo.local/pulse` → Pulse dashboard
- [ ] `https://woosoo.local/` → PWA loads (after Phase 11)

