## Common Errors & Fixes

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `HORIZON_NAME` dotenv parse error | Unquoted value with spaces | Quote it: `HORIZON_NAME="Woosoo Nexus"` |
| `bootstrap/cache` permission denied | Dir missing or wrong owner | `sudo mkdir -p /srv/woosoo/nexus/bootstrap/cache && sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /srv/woosoo/nexus/bootstrap` |
| `key:generate` permission denied | .env is 640, www-data can't write | `chmod 660 /etc/woosoo/.env`, generate, `chmod 640` |
| Supervisor ENXIO / FATAL | `/dev/stdout` in systemd context | Use file paths: `/var/log/woosoo/*.log` |
| dnsmasq `.local` not resolving | avahi intercepts before dnsmasq | Add `local=/local/` to dnsmasq.conf + `hosts: files dns mdns4` in nsswitch.conf |
| `504 Gateway Timeout` | php8.4-fpm not started | `sudo systemctl enable php8.4-fpm && sudo systemctl start php8.4-fpm` |
| `/api/config` returns `host:0.0.0.0 port:null` | BroadcastConfig using `env()` after config:cache | Fixed in code — reads from `$reverb['options']` (public_port / public_scheme keys) |
| `METHOD_NOT_ALLOWED` on a route | Code not pulled on Pi | `cd /srv/woosoo/nexus && sudo git pull && sudo -u www-data php artisan config:cache` |

